{"tid":857391,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"​騰訊暴跌，劉央或成最大贏家","createTime":"2018-10-11T05:15:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T10:52:32.000Z","uid":54870,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"58348adf3b9658312548aeddde051d8a878b1dab","tid":857391,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T05:15:49.000Z","msg":"劉央曾指，在騰訊5元及100元水平購入，但之後沽出，一直等待機會再買入，早前在騰訊跌穿405元水平大手買入，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">單日投資額高達6億元</span></span>，但不願透露總投資額。如果她中途沒有減持的話，以今日中午收市265.6元計算，累計跌34%，料輸2.06億元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年8月，本報記者致電劉央，詢問她對騰訊最新看法及會否減倉。她拒絕在電話中回應，「我不能給意見，談投資是比較嚴肅的事，我無法這樣回答。」而劉央在9月中發佈的西澤2018中期展望中提到：「我們認為所有負面影響已經反映在了股價上，最黑暗的時期已經過去。我們相信，許多股票的基本面相當穩健，而恒生指數在未來3年將實現個位數乃至雙位數的盈利增長。」"},{"pid":"1fdc66c132afef73c7bba50d672618cfa93bb96f","tid":857391,"uid":10757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T05:22:48.000Z","msg":"恒指要衰3年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8f6a75557fd8670c23d617a3b25772443489e9d","tid":857391,"uid":48526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T06:07:04.000Z","msg":"西京投資主席劉央是趨勢投資者, 現在趨勢係向下, 佢跟趨勢係好正常. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【女股神】劉央：價值投資已沒意義，不要再跟我談value<br />\n<br />\n「中國女股神」西京投資主席劉央表示，看好5大板塊，包括醫療保健股、消費股、環境相關股、科技股及金融股，每個板塊佔投資比例均超過10%。<br />\n<br />\n她指，以市盈率等衝量港股值不值得買已不合事宜，「我以前是價值投資者（value investor），但2008年之後我是趨勢投資者。」她說，現在光說價值投資已沒有意義，「銀行股P/B 0.8，印度的銀行有4點幾，難道內銀比印度的差嗎？所以不要再跟我談value。」她說，價值投資的年代已結束，再談會被時代淘汰。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180411/58058872\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180411%2F58058872&d=97fExk77nkGkdEDbKyWwYYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=46573575\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180411%2F58058872&h=5d283bed\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180411/58058872</a>"},{"pid":"3656825b7dc859e39e8f1c01a80b36024ce6669a","tid":857391,"uid":190431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b8f6a75557fd8670c23d617a3b25772443489e9d","tid":857391,"uid":48526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T06:07:04.000Z","msg":"西京投資主席劉央是趨勢投資者, 現在趨勢係向下, 佢跟趨勢係好正常. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【女股神】劉央：價值投資已沒意義，不要再跟我談value<br />\n<br />\n「中國女股神」西京投資主席劉央表示，看好5大板塊，包括醫療保健股、消費股、環境相關股、科技股及金融股，每個板塊佔投資比例均超過10%。<br />\n<br />\n她指，以市盈率等衝量港股值不值得買已不合事宜，「我以前是價值投資者（value investor），但2008年之後我是趨勢投資者。」她說，現在光說價值投資已沒有意義，「銀行股P/B 0.8，印度的銀行有4點幾，難道內銀比印度的差嗎？所以不要再跟我談value。」她說，價值投資的年代已結束，再談會被時代淘汰。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180411/58058872\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180411%2F58058872&d=97fExk77nkGkdEDbKyWwYYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=46573575\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180411%2F58058872&h=5d283bed\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180411/58058872</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T06:16:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"015d84efa02acda0e34677d464bfafa0596d0f2f","tid":857391,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T06:44:57.000Z","msg":"肥婆女燈神<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不了"},{"pid":"3ebb9b6d0be74592b56f1505818c3efbba867f28","tid":857391,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T06:46:53.000Z","msg":"女 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 神"},{"pid":"3683a9b3c2787ba3e9188f8fcfcae2795d31d7bf","tid":857391,"uid":57862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T07:00:56.000Z","msg":"大媽真勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d9651bec76e8a7a54f87b985ea530ee304a4792","tid":857391,"uid":31215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1fdc66c132afef73c7bba50d672618cfa93bb96f","tid":857391,"uid":10757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T05:22:48.000Z","msg":"恒指要衰3年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T07:12:25.000Z","msg":"點止<br />\n支爆<br />\n香港國際地位不保<br />\n基建燒錢<br />\n有排上唔返三字頭"},{"pid":"731716462187a8817556b8883f79b8140ed7896d","tid":857391,"uid":65128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T08:03:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d5afe32a39d3e63bf6f58c095f3467acd1ad67b0","tid":857391,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"731716462187a8817556b8883f79b8140ed7896d","tid":857391,"uid":65128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T08:03:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T10:50:37.000Z","msg":"582<br />\n700<br />\n<br />\n最近兩大力作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5b2ec35d82caf3da0c5d259a2f12021101a1416","tid":857391,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T10:52:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hHo6Uku.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhHo6Uku.gif&h=9bc459ee&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}